<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A5504069003">
<title>
DTC Confirmation Procedure
</title>
<attention1>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Perform road test in a place where there is no traffic to prevent an accident.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Road test should be performed with two persons, a driver and a tester, on a level road.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention1>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
If other DTC than P1828 is newly detected during this “DTC Confirmation Procedure”, troubleshoot the newly detected DTC first.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check that the following condition is satisfied in this procedure.
</ptxt>
</item>
<list2 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
11 V &#60; Battery voltage &#60; 15 V
</ptxt>
</item>
</list2>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
With ignition OFF, connect SUZUKI scan tool to DLC.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start engine and display “Slope sensor” parameter under “Data List” of SUZUKI scan tool.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Depress accelerator pedal and drive vehicle for 15 sec. or more with “Slope Sensor” parameter at 5% or more.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A5504069004">
<title>
DTC Troubleshooting
</title>
<diag type = "test" id = "AENBP70A5504069005">
<testgroup id = "AENBP70A5504069007">
<question>
Was “CVT System Check” performed?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 2.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to “CVT System Check”.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70A5504069006">
<title>
Slope sensor check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check slope sensor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A5506041"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 3.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace slope sensor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A5506040"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70A5504069008">
<title>
DTC check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Perform 
<intxref refid = "AENBP70A5506042">Slope Sensor Calibration</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Perform DTC confirmation procedure, and check DTC.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is DTC P1828 still detected?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Substitute a known-good TCM and recheck DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A5506004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
End.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
</diag>
